Trizwit Documentation

This document contains various components we have developed using ftd language.

Below are a few sample components:

Navbar Component

We have developed the navbar component for trizwit.com, which matches the design currently displayed on the live site.
Input
null
-- lib.navbar: **Trizwit**
text-1: Home
text-2: Services
text-3: About
text-4: Contact Us
linkedin: $assets.files.images.linkedin.png
twit: $assets.files.images.twitter.png

-- lib.navbar: **Trizwit**
text-1: Home
text-2: Services
text-3: About
text-4: Contact Us
linkedin: $assets.files.images.linkedin.png
twit: $assets.files.images.twitter.png
Output
Trizwit
HomeServicesAboutContact Us

HomeServicesAboutContact Us

Process Component

We have developed the process component for trizwit.com, which matches the design currently displayed on the live site.
Input
null
-- lib.process:

-- lib.process:
Output
Ideation
We discuss the feasibility of your blockchain project with our blockchain developers and define the business goals and workflow for your system
Assessment
We analyze your existing solution and discover if it can be migrated to the blockchain.
Technical Component Definition
Our blockchain consulting team identifies the right blockchain platform based on your business requirements and the type of blockchain.
PoC
We create a framework and prototype to identify the use cases for the business with minimum viable features.
Integration
Our Blockchain Consultants help clients identify if the blockchain technology can be integrated into their business operations and environment.define the business goals and workflow for your system
Development
Once you are ready to start blockchain technology development, we help you build the blockchain product, from UI/UX to full front-end and back-end implementation
